\section{Results}
\subsection{Descriptive Statistics}
\subsubsection{Summary Tables}

\section{Conclusion}
\subsection{Implications}
\subsubsection{Future Work}

\end{document}
```
After compiling the document twice, the TOC will be generated as follows:

